[recv] {"type": "message_end", "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "thinking", "thinking": "**Examining Native Image reflection**\n\nI'm thinking about how Native Image works without metadata in context with annotations. It seems like the GraalVM native-image JUnit might not capture all private fields or methods. JCommander parses with `cls.getDeclaredFields`, and I wonder about metadata for reachable classes in Native Image. I realize that `Class.getDeclaredFields` will return empty unless those fields are registered, so I need to figure out how reflection limitations impact test classes and inner fields. There's a lot to consider here!", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_0a2f94c4ef558daa0169f62347925081978ce8392f97c26500\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp9iNWC-Opto4pUgu_ufELQWhX50ZQrbuTV9WQY2PHx0pXxt1u8f8m6swVRP0Jdz9Ss9z-KZz9EacG3N75m_7-bVRpo8ryrl0ad-05yTIP6e_0TkTkAFTVpzTC8D3HUwz94z54JlqfRXa3XipdYZgaTzDcVT8QA2q99pxGFxSvMahIq4TvHZ7adqUukajBMq9QokUB135Xu3EDRCQdF_u2SENad86OTbz9Fl2x81e-Eu4d40WdOoW9ECdZd5m8j106PVMCqPsk9iyKEDTEFFYo2H-OA6Cgbbfw03w76tV02ck23v5dg7iDJCj0NAaMJbGQuCTInAiqIpdq_76_PBTBnSI3W1dDO0qA7pUdMnY5GO3Xs-Dc2rLLn5CZbp0dpGBhHvibIrTfLmWr38cGAc7uYYnWWdKF3pwO2bKK4NaN6G4623HjVMYobUMmrVfBMRkycibEscOds3ppfiSafmKQVlaT-ynJZ2lXmzIKmZ4TOrxAiQVeeF5Clow9tt2FFtNPBcSZz8ZTu4YTbaTPJBWOOVthubTG6AK4lGlqG_Kg4GpZPygj3IDRQdfB7x1plPi0mXvREBhoZ54TJkHIbdWdM3KmOoPzzKqEUNW_PHoV5mte-raIrzKWd71HCMpCmc06wZ8vgGH8owEB2xZoUaAloOAoWLQSkSNOEqpwgx3TCD8wUrRJaQU_-l7q1hkSQc_JRhC4gWU3F8FDza0FLC3bmnMaEZaXkGvV4wPALiiPJRHastVky_u4ENOgQGouoNA8zpdKJCtMXygtmKMIXWmG9neNd-A6ZzyFURRl7MRknClGogPn8PvkfnPReYcNxsD2msogUOuYWt21YUL2S0yMWcbHE9HkQnWJPHmneRtcR5-zgRVGHY2uhpswNCwYbgi-LEH6b9oe6oSH62mYT2VjhHXZcrt3EDiVo_Tzcj1VH-sxNSm_xtkfosaBfN9WsZWTacj89xT_9aMR4IwXiU-qbFX1ymidTglZ8So7zlTPNVRCzshZaxxw2jjUp_KuXPDWelphLTa_p-ERMWoZwbn_6DmMIGYBuILxFdZyNq6QxLDGUIF4RQc3aA1uWMkGPmriSMLYTdR3YcLRXusA1xgr_5rBCtI5lW6y6284f838RSy7IKhDl9Z3Oltc5BN2Rti60O7Z23kKEHd-rnusjzCG1cJ1QWaf4Cj6BtqbktD